<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LMS - Hutech</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Base */
        body{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #222222;
        }
        a{
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1{
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p{
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td{
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        /* Base */

        /* Layout */
        .email-wrapper{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header{
            background: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color:#ffffff;
        }
        .email-body{
            padding: 24px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer{
            background: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        /* Layout */

        /* Buttons */
        .buttons{
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        /* Buttons */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Well come to LMS Hutech</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">    
            <p>Hello <%= user.name%></p>
            <p>Thank you for resgistering with Becodemy. To activate your account, plese use
                the following activation code:
            </p>
            <h2><%= activationCode></h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a Becodemy account, plese ingnore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have my question, Please don't hesitale to contac us at
                <a href="mailto:anhdev24h@gmail.com">anhdev24h@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>